channel.title: [508] Bulby, when people log in my server they dont start at my home
channel.description:
[b]Okay i need to know the file where i start off... im using a 508 bulby base, & when people Log on my server they dont start at the normal home i made could anyone let me know how to change that? Could you tell me the file and what i should type in ctrl + F search bar to find where i change it?
~~Owner_Bryan~~[/b]

item.title: [508] Bulby, when people log in my server they dont start at my home
item.dc:creator: @davidi2 Davidi2
item.description:
@davidi2 wrote:

In the old Bulby bases, it should be either Login.java or Player.java

Do a search for the EXACT coordinates in those files (do ::coords in game to find the home coords) and see what comes up.
